%20responsible%20and%20benefited%20from%20the%20decades-long%20heist.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20former%20California%20official%20pleaded%20guilty%20to%20conspiring%20to%20steal%20more%20than%20%241.5%20million%20of%20water%2C%20but%20the%20decadeslong%20water%20heist%20case%20still%20has%20more%20questions%20than%20answers.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDennis%20Falaschi%20served%20as%20the%20general%20manager%20of%20the%20Panoche%20Water%20District%20in%20Fresno%20and%20Merced%20Counties%2C%20located%20in%20central%20California%2C%20from%20around%201986%20to%202017.%20The%20public%20water%20district%20bought%20water%20from%20the%20federal%20government%20and%20collected%20drainage%20water%20from%20farms%2C%20both%20of%20which%20it%20then%20legally%20sold%20to%20farmers%20in%20the%20area%2C%20according%20to%20a%20statement%20issued%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.justice.gov%2Fusao-edca%2Fpr%2Fformer-water-district-general-manager-pleads-guilty-conspiracy-commit-water-theft-and%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUS%20attorney's%20office%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20Eastern%20District%20of%20California%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20after%20Falaschi%20discovered%20some%20of%20the%20federally%20owned%20water%20was%20leaking%20from%20an%20old%20pipe%20into%20a%20separate%20canal%2C%20the%20pipe%20was%20modified%20so%20it%20could%20be%20open%20and%20closed%2C%20allowing%20water%20to%20be%20taken%20%26quot%3Bon%20demand%2C%26quot%3B%20prosecutors%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20attorney%20said%20Falaschi%20was%20responsible%20for%20stealing%20somewhere%20between%20%241.5%20million%20and%20%243.5%20million%20worth%20of%20water.%20Prosecutors%20also%20said%20that%20between%202011%20and%202016%20Falaschi%20was%20paid%20for%20water%20that%20he%20had%20sourced%20legally%2C%20but%20he%20did%20not%20report%20the%20income%20on%20his%20tax%20returns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.justice.gov%2Fusao-edca%2Fmedia%2F1353436%2Fdl%