%20certainly%20built%20for%20all%20of%20the%20wear%20and%20tear%20nightlife%20has%20to%20offer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EWorth%20a%20look%3A%3C%2Fh3%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOutdoor%20furniture%20FAQs%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20are%20common%20materials%20for%20outdoor%20furniture%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EOutdoor%20furniture%20can%20be%20made%20with%20a%20variety%20of%20materials.%20Aluminum%2C%20metal%2C%20and%20wrought%20iron%20are%20quite%20popular.%20Wood%2C%20whether%20it's%20teak%20or%20hardwood%2C%20is%20common%2C%20too.%20Wicker%2C%20eucalyptus%2C%20and%20bamboo%20are%20more%20natural-looking%20materials%2C%20while%20plastic%20and%20synthetic%20resin%20are%20typically%20considered%20cheaper%20outdoor%20furniture%20materials.%20Cushions%20are%20made%20with%20a%20variety%20of%20textiles%2C%20most%20of%20which%20are%20either%20stain%E2%80%94and%20water-resistant%20or%20water-proof.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20long%20does%20outdoor%20furniture%20last%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EDepending%20on%20the%20material%20and%20how%20well%20you%20take%20care%20of%20it%2C%20outdoor%20furniture%20can%20last%20up%20to%2015%20or%2020%20years.%20Aluminum%2C%20wicker%2C%20wrought%20iron%2C%20hardwood%2C%20and%20teakwood%20furniture%20can%20last%20quite%20a%20long%20time%20if%20you%20properly%20maintain%20them%2C%20such%20as%20by%20storing%20them%20in%20the%20winter%2C%20giving%20the%20furniture%20fresh%20paint%20jobs%20every%20few%20years%2C%20or%20oiling%20and%20resealing%20wood.%20It's%20a%20good%20idea%20to%20store%20cushions%20inside%20when%20not%20in%20use%20to%20protect%20them%20from%20the%20elements%20and%20animals.%20Furniture%20placed%20under%20a%20patio%20covering%20may%20also%20last%20longer%20than%20those%20exposed%20to%20the%20rain%20and%20sun.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20do%20you%20store%20outdoor%20furniture%20in%20the%20winter%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20thing%20you%20can%20do%20in%20the%20winter%20is%20to%20bring%20outdoor%20furniture%20indoors%2C%20be%20it%20a%20garage%2C%20shed%2C%20or%20storage%20unit.%20We%20understand%20that%20not%20everyone%20has%20the%20space%20or%20even%20the%20financial%20capabilities%20to%20do%20so.%20(At%20least%20bring%20the%20cushions%20inside!)%20You%20could%20invest%20in%20outdoor%20furniture%20covers%20or%20tarps%20that%20fully%20cover%20the%20outdoor%20pieces.%20Most%20companies%20will%20sell%20covers%20alongside%20their%20products.%20If%20you%20notice%20snow%2C%20ice%2C%20or%20leaves%20on%20the%20coverings%2C%20remove%20it%20immediately.%20If%20you%20go%20the%20cover%20or%20tarp%20route%2C%20you%20may%20want%20to%20use%20water-repellant%20spray%20on%20the%20furniture%2C%20too.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhen%20is%20the%20best%20time%20to%20buy%20outdoor%20furniture%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20will%20find%20more%20outdoor%20furniture%20options%20and%20new%20styles%20available%20at%20the%20end%20of%20spring%20and%20the%20beginning%20of%20summer.%20Shop%20early%20for%20the%20best%20selection%2C%20and%20some%20brands%20may%20have%20a%20longer%20lead%20time%20for%20delivery.%20However%2C%20if%20you're%20looking%20for%20the%20best%20outdoor%20furniture%20deals%2C%20the%20end%20of%20the%20summer%20is%20the%20best%20time%20to%20find%20the%20lowest%20prices%20as%20retailers%20make%20way%20for%20their%20fall%20inventory%2C%20though%20you%20could%20find%20some%20great%20deals%20on%20outdoor%20furniture%20around%20holidays%20like%20Memorial%20Day%20and%20Independence%20Day.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-places-buy-outdoor-patio-furniture-online%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717016263000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66577f0ecc442a2f676bf598%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F