20the%20end%20of%20the%20day.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20celebrities%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeghan-markle-green-heeled-boots-snow-outfit-photos-2019-2%5C%22%3EMeghan%20Markle%3C%2Fa%3E%20love%20these%20comfortable%20heels.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFit%20notes%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EHow%20comfortable%20this%20heel%20is%20for%20you%20depends%20on%20how%20well%20your%20feet%20fit%20the%20mold%20of%20the%20cushioned%20footbed.%20I%20also%20tried%20the%20block%20heel%20along%20with%20this%20shoe%2C%20and%20the%20arch%20of%20my%20foot%20was%20too%20high%20to%20sit%20comfortably%20on%20the%20footbed.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20my%20foot%20kept%20slipping%20out%20of%20place%20so%20I%20got%20lots%20of%20blisters.%20I%20think%20that%20the%20pump%20fit%20me%20a%20lot%20better%20because%20the%20closed%20toe%20forced%20my%20foot%20to%20stay%20in%20the%20right%20place.%20Unfortunately%2C%20the%20only%20thing%20you%20can%20do%20to%20make%20sure%20your%20foot%20fits%20the%20mold%20and%20stays%20in%20place%20is%20to%20test%20it%20for%20yourself.%20Just%20make%20sure%20that%20you%20return%20it%20within%2021%20days%20if%20it%20doesn't%20work%20for%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20heeled%20boot%3A%20Inez%20Pilar%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223737%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Inez%20Pilar%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655cec529c7d23cb3b9e1ffd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222803%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESamantha%20Crozier%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInez%20is%20a%20brand%20that%20focuses%20just%20as%20much%20on%20construction%20as%20it%20does%20on%20style.%20We%20tested%20a%20bunch%20of%20Inez's%20heels%20%E2%80%94%20and%20nearly%20all%20of%20them%20are%20winners.%20But%20this%20platform%20heeled%20boot%20was%20a%20huge%20standout%20for%20me.%20It's%20a%20full%20four%20inches%20high%20and%20yet%20it's%20incredibly%20stable%2C%20su