0was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20was%20asked%20about%20the%20activist%20claiming%20that%20the%20calls%20were%20made%20to%20favour%20the%20accused%20and%20demanding%20that%20his%20phone%20records%20be%20checked%2C%20Mr%20Pawar%20said%20in%20Marathi%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20ready%20for%20a%20narco%20test%20but%2C%20if%20I%20am%20cleared%2C%20you%20(Ms%20Damania)%20should%20stay%20quiet%20at%20home%20and%20take%20%3Cem%3E'sanyas'%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Is%20she%20ready%20for%20that%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EColleagues%20In%20Dock%20Too%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20deputy%20chief%20minister's%20comments%20came%20on%20a%20day%20when%20the%20dean%20of%20Sassoon%20Hospital%20-%20%C2%A0where%20two%20doctors%20were%20arrested%20for%20allegedly%20replacing%20the%20teenager's%20blood%20samples%20to%20ensure%20that%20no%20alcohol%20was%20detected%20in%20them%20-%20claimed%20that%20a%20minister%20and%20an%20MLA%20from%20Mr%20Pawar's%20party%20had%20written%20a%20letter%20asking%20for%20one%20of%20the%20doctors%20to%20be%20made%20the%20head%20of%20the%20forensics%20department.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Vinayak%20Kale%20claimed%20that%20the%20letter%20was%20written%20by%20Maharashtra%20Medical%20Education%20Minister%20Hasan%20Mushrif%20and%20MLA%20Sunil%20Tingre%20in%20favour%20of%20Dr%20Ajay%20Tawade%2C%20who%20was%20suspended%20as%20the%20head%20of%20the%20hospital's%20Forensic%20Medicine%20Department%20on%20Wednesday%20.%20Mr%20Tingre%20is%20already%20in%20the%20eye%20of%20a%20storm%20for%20visiting%20the%20police%20station%20where%20the%20teenager%20was%20taken%20after%20the%20accident%20on%20May%2019%20to%20allegedly%20pressure%20officials%20into%20going%20easy%20on%20the%20case.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Kale%20was%20later%20sent%20on%20compulsory%20leave%20by%20the%20Maharashtra%20government%20for%20%26quot%3Bfailing%20to%20take%20the%20case%20seriously%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bnot%20taking%20proper%20decisions%26quot%3B%20as%20the%20dean.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20May%2018%2C%20the%2017-year-old%20son%20of%20a%20prominent%20Pune%20realtor%20had%20gone%20partying%20-%20in%20a%20Rs%202.5-crore%20Porsche%20-%20with%20his%20friends%20to%20celebrate%20his%20Class%2012%20results.%20They%20went%20to%20two%20pubs%20and%20drank%20illegally%2C%20paying%20a%20bill%20of%20Rs%2048%2C000%20at%20one%20of%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20teen%20then%20got%20into%20the%20Porsche%20with%20two%20of%20his%20friends%20and%20crashed%20into%20a%20scooter%20in%20Kalyani%20Nagar%20at%20a%20speed%20of%20at%20least%20150%20kmph%20in%20the%20early%20hours%20of%20May%2019%2C%20killing%20two%2024-year-old%20IT%20professionals%20on%20the%20spot.%20Aneesh%20Awadhiya%2C%20who%20was%20riding%20the%20bike%20was%20sent%20flying%20and%20hit%20a%20parked%20car%2C%20while%20Ashwini%20Koshta%20-%20who%20was%20riding%20pillion%20-%20was%20flung%2020%20feet%20into%20the%20air.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20teenager%20had%20got%20bail%20the%20same%20day%20and%20was%20asked%20to%20write%20a%20300-word%20essay%20as%20one%20of%20the%20conditions.%20Three%20days%20later%2C%20after%20nationwide%20outrage%2C%20he%20was%20sent%20to%20a%20remand%20home%20till%20June%205.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717003680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fd9he2lbg_ajit-pawar_625x300_10_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpune-porsche-case-pune-porsche-accident-will-she-take-sanyas-ajit-pawar-on-activists-pressure-claims-in-porsche-case-5774133%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Reacting%20sharply%20to%20an%20activist's%20claims%20that%20he%20had%20called%20the%20Pune%20police%20commissioner%20to%20%26quot%3Bpressure%20him%26quot%3B%20after%20the%20Pune%20Porsche%20accident%2C%20Maharashtra%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Ajit%20Pawar%20has%20said%20he%20is%20ready%20to%20take%20a%20narco%20test.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%2