D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Citizenship%20Certificates%20Under%20CAA%20Given%20To%20Beneficiaries%20In%20Bengal%3A%20Centre%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ELess%20than%20two%20weeks%20after%20the%20first%20set%20of%20citizenship%20certificates%20were%20issued%20under%20the%20Citizenship%20(Amendment)%20Act%2C%20the%20process%20has%20also%20begun%20in%20West%20Bengal%2C%20where%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20law%20has%20been%20a%20contentious%20issue.%20The%20Union%20Home%20Ministry%20said%20Empowered%20Committees%20of%20the%20States%20of%20Haryana%20and%20Uttarakhand%20have%20also%20granted%20citizenship%20to%20the%20first%20set%20of%20applicants.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Citizenship%20(Amendment)%20Act%20(CAA)%20was%20enacted%20in%20December%202019%20to%20grant%20Indian%20citizenship%20to%20persecuted%20non-Muslim%20migrants%20from%20Pakistan%2C%20Afghanistan%20and%20Bangladesh.%20It%20reduced%20the%20qualification%20period%20for%20Hindus%2C%20Jains%2C%20Christians%2C%20Sikhs%2C%20Buddhists%20and%20Parsis%20from%20these%20countries%2C%20who%20came%20to%20India%20on%20or%20before%20December%2031%2C%202014%2C%20from%20eleven%20years%20to%20five.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CAA%20rules%20were%20notified%20only%20in%20March%20this%20year%2C%20however%2C%20after%20massive%20protests%20stalled%20its%20implementation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20election%20speeches%20in%20West%20Bengal%2C%20PM%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20attacked%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20(TMC)%20over%20the%20issue%20and%20alleged%20that%20%26quot%3Binfiltrators%26quot%3B%20are%20flourishing%20in%20the%20state%20under%20the%20party's%20rule.%20He%20repeated%20the%20charge%20earlier%20on%20Wednesday%20as%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20demography%20in%20the%20border%20areas%20of%20Bengal%20is%20being%20changed.%20The%20TMC%20is%20against%20giving%20citizenship%20to%20religiously%20persecuted%20minorities.%20Why%20are%20they%20opposing%20the%20CAA%20so%20much%3F%20Why%20are%20these%20people%20(TMC%20leaders)%20lying%20about%20the%20CAA%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20asked%20at%20a%20rally%20in%20Bengal's%20Kakdwip%2C%20his%20last%20for%20the%20ongoing%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClaiming%20that%20the%20party%20does%20not%20want%20the%20Hindus%20and%20the%20Matua%20community%20to%20stay%20in%20Bengal%2C%20the%20PM%20added%2C%20%C2%A0%26quot%3BTo%20appease%20a%20section%20of%20the%20society%2C%20the%20TMC%20government%20is%20openly%20attacking%20the%20Constitution%2C%20which%20has%20given%20reservations%20to%20Dalits%20and%20backward%20castes.%20Reservations%20were%20looted%20in%20West%20Bengal%20and%20false%20OBC%20certificates%20were%20issued%20to%20Muslims.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHitting%20back%2C%20West%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20she%20was%20%26quot%3Bready%20to%20sacrifice%20her%20life%26quot%3B%20but%20would%20not%20allow%20the%20%26quot%3Bdivisive%20politics%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20BJP%20such%20as%20the%20CAA%2C%20National%20Register%20of%20Citizens%20(NRC)%20and%20the%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20(UCC)%20in%20the%20state.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20rally%20at%20Metiabruz%20in%20the%20Diamond%20Harbour%20constituency%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20she%20reiterated%20she%20would%20not%20allow%20the%20implementation%20of%20these%20policies.%20%26quot%3BIf%20people%20do%20not%20want%20divisive%20CAA%2C%20NRC%20or%20UCC%20that%20will%20erase%20our%20diversity%2C%20they%20must%20vote%20against%20the%20BJP%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Home%20Ministry%20said%20the%20first%20set%20of%20applicants%20from%20West%20Bengal%20were%20granted%20citizenship%20by%20the%20state's%20empowered%20committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSimilarly%2C%20the%20Empowered%20Committees%20of%20the%20States%20of%20Haryana%20and%20Uttarakhand%20have%20also%20granted%20citizenship%20today%20to%20the%20first%20set%20of%20applicants%20in%20their%20respective%20States%2