h-african-elections-why-nelson-mandelas-party-could-lose-its-dominance-13145125%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20China%20Is%20Helping%20Pakistan%20In%20PoK%20With%20Military%20Supplies%20Along%20LoC%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPakistan's%20key%20ally%20China%20has%20been%20actively%20bolstering%20the%20defence%20capabilities%20of%20the%20Pakistani%20army%20along%20the%20Line%20of%20Control%20(LoC)%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20over%20the%20past%20three%20years%20which%20includes%20the%20construction%20of%20steelhead%20bunkers%20and%20the%20provision%20of%20Unmanned%20Aerial%20and%20Combat%20Aerial%20Vehicles%2C%20officials%20said%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChinese%20assistance%20in%20Pakistan-occupied%20Kashmir%20or%20PoK%20also%20extends%20to%20the%20installation%20of%20highly%20encrypted%20communication%20towers%20and%20the%20laying%20of%20underground%20fibre%20cables%20along%20the%20Line%20of%20Control%20(LoC).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20advanced%20radar%20systems%20of%20Chinese%20origin%2C%20such%20as%20the%20'JY'%20and%20'HGR'%20series%2C%20have%20been%20deployed%20to%20enhance%20medium%20and%20low%20altitude%20target%20detection%20capabilities%2C%20providing%20crucial%20intelligence%20support%20for%20army%20and%20air%20defence%20units%2C%20officials%20told%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20the%20presence%20of%20the%20SH-15%2C%20a%20155%20mm%20truck-mounted%20howitzer%20gun%20manufactured%20by%20a%20Chinese%20firm%2C%20has%20been%20noticed%20at%20various%20locations%20along%20the%20LoC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20move%20is%20seen%20as%20part%20of%20efforts%20to%20strengthen%20China's%20ties%20with%20Pakistan%20and%20safeguard%20Chinese%20investments%20in%20Pakistan-occupied%20Kashmir%2C%20particularly%20related%20to%20the%20so-called%20'China-Pakistan%20Economic%20Corridor'%20or%20'CPEC'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20presence%20of%20senior%20PLA%20officials%20at%20forward%20posts%2C%20as%20was%20detected%20in%202014%2C%20was%20not%20found%2C%20some%20intercepts%20suggested%20that%20Chinese%20troops%20and%20engineers%20were%20setting%20up%20infrastructure%20along%20the%20LoC%2C%20including%20building%20underground%20bunkers%2C%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChinese%20experts%20were%20engaged%20in%20tunnel%20construction%20in%20the%20Leepa%20Valley%20of%20Pakistan-occupied%20Kashmir%20(PoK)%2C%20signalling%20preparations%20for%20an%20all-weather%20road%20to%20connect%20with%20the%20Karakoram%20highway%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20strategic%20move%20is%20linked%20to%20Beijing's%20ambitious%2046-billion-dollar%20so-called%20'CPEC'%20project%2C%20aiming%20to%20establish%20a%20direct%20route%20between%20Gwadar%20Port%20in%20Balochistan%20and%20Xinjiang%2C%20occupied%20by%20China%2C%20through%20the%20Karakoram%20highway%2C%20an%20area%20under%20the%20illegal%20occupation%20of%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202007%2C%20a%20Chinese%20telecom%20company%20had%20taken%20over%20a%20Pakistani%20telecom%20company%20and%20formed%20China%20Mobile%20Pakistan%20(CMPak)%20-%20a%20100%20per%20cent%20owned%20subsidiary%20of%20China%20Mobile%20Communications%20Corporation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20August%202022%2C%20the%20Pakistan%20Telecommunication%20Authority%20(PTA)%2C%20while%20renewing%20the%20mobile%20licence%20of%20CMPak%20(Zong)%20for%20PoK%2C%20gave%20permission%20to%20expand%20Next%20Generation%20Mobile%20Services%20(NGMS)%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Indian%20Army%20has%20maintained%20silence%20on%20the%20matter%2C%20intelligence%20agencies%20are%20reportedly%20being%20kept%20informed%20of%20the%20developments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20continuous%20presence%20of%20Chinese%20military%20personnel%20in%20the%20region%20has%20raised%20concerns%2C%20with%20India%20voicing%20objections%20to%20Chinese%20activities%20in%20Gilgit%20and%20Baltistan%20areas%20in%20PoK%20in%20the%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20tensions%20persist%2C%20India%20remains%20vigilant%20and%20prepared%20to%20thwart%20any%20potential%20threats%20emanating%20from%20across%20the%20border%2C%20officials%20told%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716993660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2018-09%2Fi3hf8gi8_xi-jinping-reuters_625x300_22_September_18.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhow-china-is-helping-pakistan-in-pok-with-military-supplies-along-loc-report-5770916%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pakistan's%20key%20ally%20China%20has%20been%20actively%20bolstering%20the%20defence%20capabilities%20of%20the%20Pakistani%20army%20along%20the%20Line%20of%20Control%20(LoC)%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20over%20the%20past%20three%20years.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhow-china-is-helping-pakistan-in-pok-with-military-supplies-along-loc-report-5770916%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhow-china-is-helping-pakistan-in-pok-with-military-supplies-along-loc-report-5770916%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhow-china-is-helping-pakistan-in-pok-with-military-supplies-along-loc-report-5770916%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Got%20Death%20Threats%20For%20Criticising%20Kohli%3A%20IPL%20Commentator%2C%20Karthik%20Responds%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20New%20Zealand%20pacer%20Simon%20Doull%20has%20revealed%20that%20he%20has%20been%20receiving%20death%20threats%20for%20his%20criticism%20of%20India%20and%20Royal%20Challengers%20Bengaluru%20(RCB)%20batter%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Virat%20Kohli%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F967-virat-kohli-playerprofile%5C%22%3EVirat%20Kohli%3C%2Fa%3E.%20While%20the%20cricketer-turned-commentator%20has%20often%20labelled%20Kohli%20as%20the%20greatest%20batter%20of%20his%20generation%2C%20he%20also%20doesn't%20shy%20away%20from%20criticising%20him%20whenever%20he%20needs%20to.%20As%20an%20observer%20of%20the%20game%2C%20Doull%20was%20one%20of%20several%20former%20players%20who%20had%20criticised%20Kohli%20for%20his%20batting%20strike%20rate%20during%20the%20initial%20phase%20of%20IPL%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKohli%20had%20also%20voiced%20his%20anger%20over%20the%20criticism%20of%20his%20batting%20approach%2C%20saying%20that%20he%20doesn't%20like%20people%20to%20tell%20him%20how%20to%20construct%20him%2C%20considering%20that%20he%20has%20been%20winning%20games%20for%20over%20a%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20RCB's%20wait%20for%20an%20IPL%20title%20continued%2C%20Kohli%20ended%20the%20season%20as%20the%20highest%20run-getter.%20He%20scored%20741%20runs%20in%2015%20matches%20at%20an%20average%20of%20154.7.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20a%20discussion%2C%20Kohli's%20RCB%20teammate%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Dinesh%20Karthik%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F666-dinesh-karthik-playerprofile%5C%22%3EDinesh%20Karthik%3C%2Fa%3E%20suggested%20that%20the%20star%20batter%20thrives%20in%20such%20situations%20as%20he%20likes%20to%20prove%20his%20critics%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVirat%20Kohli%20would%20like%20to%20write%20a%20book%20on%20how%20he%20was%20this%20year.%20He%20started%20okay.%20Thanks%20to%20people%20like%20Simon%20(Doull)%20and%20a%20few%20others%20who%20really%20spurred%20him%20on.%20And%20you%20know%20that%20side%20of%20Virat%20Kohli.%20I%20think%20that%20he%20thrives%20on%20that.%20He%20is%20someone%20who%20inadvertently%20holds%20on%20to%20certain%20things%20to%20do%20well.%20He%20loves%20people%20proving%20wrong.%20Even%20though%20he%20might%20not%20come%20out%20and%20say%20this%2C%20it%20really%20fuels%20his%20passion.%20He%20is%20like%20a%20molten%20lava%20coming%20out.%20He%20is%20fiery%20and%20you%20don't%20want%20to%20be%20anywhere%20close%20to%20him%20because%20you%20are%20going%20to%20get%20burnt%20for%20sure%2C%26quot%3B%20Karthik%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3PeYKSPdjm0%5C%22%3ECricbuzz%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20the%20IPL%202024%20final%20with%20Doull%20also%20part%20of%20the%20discussion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDoull%20emphasised%20that%20nobody%20really%20cares%20when%20he%20praises%20Kohli%2C%20but%20a%20minor%20criticism%20of%20the%20star%20batter%20often%20leads%20to%20him%20getting%20death%20threats%20from%20the%20so%20called%20fans%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe's%20too%20good%20to%20worry%20about%20what%20if%20he%20gets%20out.%20He's%20too%20good%20a%20player%2C%20and%20that%20was%20always%20my%20point%20around%20him.%20I%20said%20a%20thousand%20great%20things%20about%20Virat%20Kohli%2C%20but%20I%20say%20one%20thing%20that%20might%20be%20slightly%20negative%20or%20construed%20to%20be%20negative%2C%20I%20get%20death%20threats%2C%26quot%3B%20Doull%20pointed%20out%20during%20the%20same%20discussion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDoull%20further%20suggested%20that%20he%20has%20nothing%20personal%20against%20Kohli%20as%20he%20often%20speaks%20to%20him%20before%20or%20after%20the%20games.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20never%20personal.%20We've%20had%20great%20conversations.%20I've%20interviewed%20him%20at%20tosses%2C%20we've%20talked%20after%20games%2C%20there's%20never%20been%20an%20issue.%20It's%20the%20same%20thing%20I%20said%20about%20Babar%20and%20talked%20to%20him%20after%20the%20game.%20He%20also%20told%20me%20that%20the%20coach%20had%20said%20that%20same%20to%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKarthik%20condemned%20the%20death%20threats%20against%20Doull%2C%20urging%20the%20Indian%20fans%20to%20find%20the%20difference%20between%20constructive%20criticism%20and%20someone%20taki