2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAanchal%E2%80%99s%20story%20is%20more%20than%20just%20an%20individual%E2%80%99s%20triumph%20over%20adversity%2C%20it%20is%20a%20powerful%20call%20to%20action%20for%20building%20a%20truly%20inclusive%20society.%20By%20promoting%20accessibility%20awareness%20and%20implementing%20robust%20support%20systems%2C%20we%20can%20empower%20everyone%20regardless%20of%20ability%20to%20reach%20their%20full%20potential.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnchal%E2%80%99s%20journey%20is%20just%20one%20of%20the%20many.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F343534%2Fsparsh-asian-paints-start-foundation-initiative-tactile-art-rajasthan-netraheen-kalyan-sangh-jaipur%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPeople%20with%20diverse%20disabilities%20benefit%20from%20digital%20accessibility%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20can%20be%20found%20in%20a%20number%20of%20different%20forms.%20From%20adaptive%20keyboards%20to%20speech%20to%20text%20softwares%2C%20technology%20has%20come%20a%20long%20way%20in%20finding%20ways%20to%20accommodate%20human%20diversity%2C%20all%20that%20is%20remaining%20is%20a%20sincere%20effort%20from%20us%20to%20integrate%20it%20into%20our%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWritten%20by%20V-shesh%2C%20edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716888992000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FInfographic-website-5-1716877656.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D351275%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Anchal%20Bhateja%20lost%20her%20eyesight%20just%20before%20her%20board%20exams.%20She%20chose%20to%20keep%20her%20dreams%20alive%20and%20worked%20twice%20as%20hard%20as%20her%20peers%20to%20become%20a%20lawyer.%20Here's%20how%20she%20and%20others%20like%20her%20found%20their%20way%20in%20life%20using%20screen%20readers%20and%20other%20such%20tools%20of%20digital%20inclus