ies%20the%20locals%20of%20Ladakh%20faced.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20shocked%20to%20learn%20that%20the%20villagers%20walked%2035%20km%20for%20a%20litre%20of%20oil.%20Imagine%20walking%20for%20five%20hours%20for%20a%20single%20litre!%E2%80%9D%20Appalled%2C%20she%20began%20approaching%20the%20authorities%20for%20an%20oil%20extraction%20machine%2C%20and%20within%20months%20the%20villagers%E2%80%99%20woes%20were%20eased.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20ask%20was%20delivered%2C%20their%20smiles%20were%20all%20the%20validation%20she%20looked%20for.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fguna-organics-1-1716442986.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20solar%20dryers%20are%20a%20step%20towards%20encouraging%20the%20farmers%20of%20Ladakh%20to%20sell%20the%20preserved%20fruits%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fguna-organics-1-1716442986.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fguna-organics-1-1716442986-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fguna-organics-1-1716442986-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fguna-organics-1-1716442986-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fguna-organics-1-1716442986-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-350872%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20solar%20dryers%20are%20a%20step%20towards%20encouraging%20the%20farmers%20of%20Ladakh%20to%20sell%20the%20preserved%20fruits%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Vishwadeep%20Trust%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-h