Among%20the%20major%20health%20issues%20in%20livestock%20were%20productivity%20and%20difficulties%20in%20pregnancies%20owing%20to%20malnutrition.%20We%20provide%20herbal%20treatment%20that%20boosts%20suitable%20ovulation%20period%20in%20cattle.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FManish-Prahlad-3-1716381268.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Verdant%20Impact%20is%20associated%20with%20more%20than%20six%20lakh%20farmers.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FManish-Prahlad-3-1716381268.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FManish-Prahlad-3-1716381268-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FManish-Prahlad-3-1716381268-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FManish-Prahlad-3-1716381268-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FManish-Prahlad-3-1716381268-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-350780%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EVerdant%20Impact%20is%20associated%20with%20more%20than%20six%20lakh%20farmers.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20instance%2C%20bovines%20usually%20conceive%20in%2037%20to%2040%20months%20if%20it%20is%20malnourished%20but%20when%20you%20provide%20good%20nutrition%2C%20they%20are%20ready%20to%20conceive%20in%2022%20to%2027%20months.%20This%20gives%20farmers%20an%20extra%20cycle%20for%20gestation%20before%20the%20bovine%20is%20ready%20for%20the%20next%20calving.%20Depending%20on%20the%20breed%2C%20they%20earn%20an%20extra%20income%20of%20up%20to%20Rs%202%20to%203%20lakh%20annually%2C%E2%